Title: To Rambleshire
Description:
There's word of troubles in the village of Rambleshire, at the base of Thunderhead Peak. 

Can't abide the place myself. Always wet and rumbling.

But Rooktender Lufsela thought it worth a look, however, seeing as how the birds fancy the moss that the village produces. She's still green though, and might just need a hand.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Meet Lufsela at the entrance to Rambleshire
RewardText:
Otwin sent you? Probably misses my help brushing out the rooks. But there's something amiss here in Rambleshire.

There should be a storm overhead. Been visible from Dornogal for as long as I can remember. Without that storm, I fear the local mosswool operation is in trouble.
